{"tid":1689641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Rickard Scotford今早發PO：北京淡化香港成為國際傳媒關注點，用警察國家製造恐佈主義鎮壓","createTime":"2019-11-03T02:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T07:30:58.000Z","uid":323575,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"fc184887ddcb91f06a1459092c4d15226cce2502","tid":1689641,"uid":323575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"他今朝發的長文PO<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/posts/2100453326722639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRichScotford5%2Fposts%2F2100453326722639&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=63e5d057\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/posts/2100453326722639</a><br />\n要點：<br />\n1. 警暴昨天升級，明顯警隊只聽命北京<br />\n2. 狗不當示威者是人，這是中共願意看見的，目的是殘殺香港人<br />\n3. 港共要巿民感到在街頭有示威者或者黑警都是危險、不法及有暴力場面<br />\n4. 狗警現在所做一切並非檢控及送人上法庭，而是製造恐佈主義<br />\n<br />\n最後，他認為北京深明香港若再成為國際傳媒頭版的事件，除了百萬人遊行，亦有三個可能：一個解決方法、解放軍進城、屠殺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">北京不妥協、不解決、不出解於軍</span></span></strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更重要的是不讓百萬人同時、同地、同日上街</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共成功地使令狗警每日讓香港人生活在惶恐之中已足夠</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人反抗</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a2402524b500022a3be7294bb253412a824dd5b7","tid":1689641,"uid":6363,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":